{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2555570/extras/title-about-en.png?t=1738629169\" /><br><br>Age of Goblins is a casual RTS inspired by some classics of the genre, bringing chaos to the battlefield with frantic matches and a lot of tactical mastery while simplifying controls and mechanics, allowing you to sit down and have fun right away without spending hours learning how to play.<br><br>Your goal is to lead an expanding goblin tribe and conquer all stages, extinguishing rival tribes and keeping everything for yourself. It may sound a bit selfish, but they will also do everything to make you disappear from the map (literally), and you can't just stand there watching while arrows fly everywhere, right?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2555570/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1738629169\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2555570/extras/title-features.png?t=1738629169\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Tactical Expansion:</strong> Conquer new caves, towers, and farms to grow your small empire of little creatures.<br><br></li><li><strong>Manage your stocks:</strong> Without food, goblins don't reproduce. Gather from nature or cultivate your own.<br><br></li><li><strong>Dozens of maps:</strong> Individually hand-drawn, with various biomes and different strategies for victory.<br><br></li><li><strong>Earn blessings:</strong> The gods reward those who do well in battle. Use abilities to turn the game in your favor.<br><br></li><li><strong>Chaotic pace:</strong> Hundreds of units crossing the map and invading your territories.<br><br></li><li><strong>Personal record:</strong> Record your best times and try new tactics to improve your performance.<br><br></li><li><strong>Build your tribe:</strong> Nothing like going to war with some visual customizations. It's good for self-esteem.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2555570/extras/customize-tribe.gif?t=1738629169\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2555570/extras/title-warning-en.png?t=1738629169\" /><br><br>Don't be fooled by the cute visuals. Despite having simple commands, Age of Goblins can require a lot of agility and quick decision-making at times, just like the good old classic RTS games.<br>Some maps can be really challenging, so keep that in mind before playing, okay?!<br><br>* This is the dev's first published game, made solo and with a lot of love over the course of a year. By purchasing it, you contribute to the creation of new games and new experiences. My heartfelt thanks...<br><br>and may your tribe triumph!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2555570/extras/title-rodape.png?t=1738629169\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Apprentice Conqueror","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2555570/0f72c50c6fb7628584c1967cf0c1ca72a594676c.jpg"},{"name":"Experienced Conqueror","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2555570/f52b4587a55b40cfb6f5bee99ee645fd8ed6c4f4.jpg"},{"name":"Master Conqueror","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2555570/42118719d05b24a83bfb8c23db35359c623cb12f.jpg"},{"name":"Apprentice Farmer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2555570/ad1ec322caa2b24ef4803bf405c2b3016ca746da.jpg"},{"name":"Experienced Farmer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2555570/e01aff9daff9b2235b8343d134637f77b69cddd9.jpg"},{"name":"Master Farmer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2555570/f0aba4593fc47f81154aab62db917cc